                            <comment id="12613293" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Mon, 14 Jul 2008 11:19:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Agreed that the default charset dependency needs to be removed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, I have an alternative suggestion:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the case of the Hex encode() method, one could completely avoid the need to use getBytes() by using a byte[] array for the conversion.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Likewise, I think the Hex decode() could just be performed on bytes rather than converting to char first.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch to follow.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12613299" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Mon, 14 Jul 2008 12:08:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Add byte[] conversion methods (with private toDigit(byte method)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
